Package: SCPP
Type: Package
Title: Projection Pursuit for Spectral Clustering
Version: 0.1.0
Author: David Hofmeyr <dhofmeyr@sun.ac.za> [aut, cre]
Maintainer: David Hofmeyr <dhofmeyr@sun.ac.za>
Description: Performs projection pursuit based on spectral connectivity to find optimal subspaces for spectral clustering. Clustering is performed recursively by repeatedly identifying subspaces for separating (some) clusters from others.
Depends: R (>= 2.10.0)
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: yes
Imports: rARPACK, pracma, FactoClass
